{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Spellsided is a <strong>turn-based single-player RPG</strong> that comes with a <strong>new, puzzling twist on deck-builders</strong> - it\u2019s a dice-builder!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join our Discord community and follow us on YouTube via the links in the sidebar to stay up to date with development!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/video-loadouts.gif?t=1731293429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DISCOVER SPELLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a fully-customisable magical die named Hex, who has been discarded by the Gods of the Tabletop. Cast your spells with every step as you <strong>navigate a fantasy world</strong> of toppling dominoes, warring chess pieces, and conniving cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/video-combat.gif?t=1731293429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PLAY YOUR WAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There\u2019s <strong>no correct way to solve a puzzle</strong>. Find your personal style and let your imagination run wild with the variety of loadouts and combos available!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/image-fortmino.jpg?t=1731293429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MEET FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every character has their own <strong>complex history with the Gods</strong>, either <strong>struggling to find purpose</strong>, or struggling with the purpose they\u2019ve been given. In your journey of return, you may be able to help these lost pieces... if they let you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/image-dominica.jpg?t=1731293429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIGHT ENEMIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter <strong>dozens of tricky foes</strong>, including <strong>the Dustmancer</strong>, a fallen warrior who has turned to the heretical worship of dust, revelling in godlessness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/image-challenge.jpg?t=1731293429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BEAT SCORES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test your skills in various challenge rooms placed around the world. <strong>Compare your move count</strong> with your friends and compete to finish in the <strong>lowest moves!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/video-environment.gif?t=1731293429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>IN A HAND-CRAFTED WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in a <strong>hand-made voxel fantasy realm</strong>, with stop-motion animations created frame-by-frame.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/extras/Tilda_Neutral.png?t=1731293429\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731293429","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/page.bg.jpg?t=1731293429","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088510/82c72b3c4f686d88c5bd416906c9787335a1dd41/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731293429","capsule_imagev5":"https://